Explanation: The block number in which the transaction was included
The hash of the transaction that generated this trace
The Ethereum address of the sender (originating address) of the transaction.
The Ethereum address of the recipient (destination address) of the transaction. It can be None if the transaction is creating a new contract
Number of the transactions made by the sender prior to this one
The gas price provided by the sender in Wei
The total amount of gas used when this transaction was executed in the block
